Introduction

Yubin, formerly known as Binnie, is a South Korean singer and actress signed with WM Entertainment. She is a part of the girl group OH MY GIRL and its sub-unit OH MY GIRL BANHANA.

Before debuting as an idol, she was active as a child model and actress. She began her career with the MBC drama I Love You, Don’t Cry in 2008.

On April 20, 2015, she debuted as a member of OH MY GIRL with the group’s self-titled debut mini album. She also joined the group’s special sub-unit, OH MY GIRL BANHANA, with the special album Banana Allergy Monkey on April 2, 2018.
